Little man you still look with such innocent eyes<br />
Your little feet walk with unsteady steps<br />
But time goes by and a little boy grows into a man<br />
Playing turns into grown-ups&#8217; work</p>
<p>I hope that you&#8217;ll have a big love in your heart then<br />
